{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Welcome to Maple Meadow!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Poly Rancher is an open world game where you will manage a horse ranch in the small town of Maple Meadow.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Explore the town!</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The town of Maple Meadow has much to offer - explore the town and help the townsfolk with their tasks!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398730/extras/town.png?t=1734303855\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Take care of your ranch!</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Make sure everything runs smoothly and take care of your horses and crops!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398730/extras/farmhouse.png?t=1734303855\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Raise and train horses!</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Breed horses and train them to improve their skills - some might prove trickier than others!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398730/extras/horse.png?t=1734303855\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Compete!</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Participate in horse competitions to improve your horses' skills, earn special horse traits, and earn money!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398730/extras/arenas.png?t=1734303855\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/s